{"tid":1441433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係一個深水埗街坊唔受玩火嘅原因","createTime":"2019-08-10T16:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T01:16:36.000Z","uid":140399,"like":231,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8b2872979bee486b55a9307319aae4bead762e","tid":1441433,"uid":140399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:02:27.000Z","msg":"深水埗街坊其實都好多真勇武<br />\n戰鬥力直逼黃大仙<br />\n<br />\n點解特別抗拒玩火？<br />\n<br />\n因為50年代嘅石硤尾大火！<br />\n銀髮族依家70幾就係當年小朋友<br />\n<br />\n石硤尾大火促成左港英政府起石硤尾邨原區安置<br />\n仲有之後嘅舊長沙灣邨，大坑西等<br />\n深水埗公屋幾番新，都仲有相當多深水埗街坊係當年嘅災民<br />\n佢哋好難忘記差啲唔能夠逃出生天果晚<br />\n果一晚之後佢哋足足要瞓街一年以上<br />\n<br />\n就算陰影已經處理到，都可能抗拒<br />\n<br />\n火攻絕對唔係一個無咗唔得嘅策略<br />\n勇武手足仲有好多嘢可以做<br />\n<br />\n一言以蔽之<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">保持同理心<br />\n憑人性抗爭！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n和理非對勇武要做到掉核彈都唔割蓆<br />\n都係憑同理心，憑人性！"},{"pid":"42faab47ca12ee612a9a36d9c45e8bd0d2520e22","tid":1441433,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2ec297811ee8bea176613db0b0dea0d8f87dae","tid":1441433,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37af6f4b445730c76382c1590c1895c7b31f6cb","tid":1441433,"uid":123774,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"深水埗路窄又多排檔<br />\n唔好攪到街坊生計"},{"pid":"82201ebf9f345b5e6e4a901d232cd590ef02f60a","tid":1441433,"uid":6297,"like":14,"dislike":10,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"你當抗爭者係殺人狂會周圍放火呀！都痴撚線！"},{"pid":"baf3995944879e2ca6dc6249d12426c3c60fc525","tid":1441433,"uid":78689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5956d070cb87e68d15416e747b907857b8330284","tid":1441